5. Discussion\par
The aim of this project is to help people who want to relocate to the safest borough in\par
London, expats can chose the neighborhoods to which they want to relocate based on the\par
most common venues in it. For example if a person is looking for a neighborhood with good\par
connectivity and public transportation we can see that Clusters 3 and 4 have Train stations\par
and Bus stops as the most common venues. If a person is looking for a neighborhood with\par
stores and restaurants in a close proximity then the neighborhoods in the first cluster is\par
suitable. For a family I feel that the neighborhoods in Cluster 4 are more suitable dues to\par
the common venues in that cluster, these neighborhoods have common venues such as\par
Parks, Gym/Fitness centers, Bus Stops, Restaurants, Electronics Stores and Soccer fields\par
which is ideal for a family. The choices of neighborhoods may vary from person to person.\par
